	<div id="ftn17">&#13;
		<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref17" name="_ftn17" title="" id="_ftn17"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference">[17]</span></span></a><span lang="FR-CD" xml:lang="FR-CD" xml:lang="FR-CD"> Ibid. Voir aussi Banque mondiale (Association de dveloppement international), Power Sector Recovery Project Paper, 21 fvrier 2018, http://documents.worldbank.org/curated/en/172941521424821535/pdf/GUINEA-POWER-SECTOR1-PAD-02272018.pdf, p.5 (consult le 18 novembre 2019).</span></p>&#13;
	</div>&#13;
